<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.7.11">
<l>taḻuvi niṉṟa kātaltaṉṉā ṟāmaraik kaṇṇaṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>kuḻuvu māṭat teṉkuru kūrmā ṟaṉcaṭa kōpaṉcol</l>
<l>vaḻuvi lāta voṇṭamiḻka ḷāyirattu ḷippattum</l>
<l>taḻuvap pāṭi yāṭa vallār vaikunta mēṟuvarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those able to sing [and] dance so as to embrace</l>
<l>these ten among the thousand of unswerving Tamil [stanzas]</l>
<l>spoken by Māṟaṉ Caṭakōpaṉ from southern Kurukūr with crowded mansions</l>
<l>on the one with lotus eyes, by [his] love that stands embracing [him],</l>
	<l>will rise to Vaikuntam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
